snippet.title: HUGE WIN For Johnny Depp! | Amber Heard Told To Get LOST!
snippet.description:
After three attempts to dismiss her ex-husband’s, actor Johnny Depp’s, defamation lawsuit, the Judge presiding over the case has released her verdict regarding Amber Heard’s repeated appeals.

The lawsuit regarding Heard’s allegations over domestic abuse is still set for trial next year in Fairfax County, Virginia.
